==古生態學==
[[File:Gigantoraptor_and_Alectrosaurus.jpg|thumb]]保護牠們的巢穴免受[[獨龍|獨龍]]和[[古似鳥龍|古似鳥龍]]騷擾]]
古似鳥龍遺骸發現於二連組，年代可追溯至白堊紀晚期森諾曼階，約9600萬年前。<ref name=Guo2018>{{cite journal|last1=Guo|first1=Z. X.|last2=Shi|first2=Y. P.|last3=Yang|first3=Y. T.|last4=Jiang|first4=S. Q.|last5=Li|first5=L. B.|last6=Zhao|first6=Z. G.|title=Inversion of the Erlian Basin (NE China) in the early Late Cretaceous: Implications for the collision of the Okhotomorsk Block with East Asia|date=2018|journal=Journal of Asian Earth Sciences|volume=154|pages=49–66|doi=10.1016/j.jseaes.2017.12.007|url=http://icpms.ustc.edu.cn/laicpms/publications/2018-GuoZX-JAES.pdf|access-date=2020-12-30|archive-date=2020-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919173817/http://icpms.ustc.edu.cn/laicpms/publications/2018-GuoZX-JAES.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>地層所呈現的環境是充滿[[辨狀河|辨狀河]][[曲流|曲流]]<ref name=Itterbeeck2005>{{cite journal|last1=Van Itterbeeck|first1=J.|last2=Horne|first2=D. J.|last3=Bultynck|first3=P.|last4=Vandenberghe|first4=N.|year=2005|title=Stratigraphy and palaeoenvironment of the dinosaur-bearing Upper Cretaceous Iren Dabasu Formation, Inner Mongolia, People's Republic of China|url=https://www.academia.edu/3856254|journal=Cretaceous Research|volume=26|issue=4|pages=699–725|doi=10.1016/j.cretres.2005.03.004|access-date=2020-12-30|archive-date=2021-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211205063149/https://www.academia.edu/3856254}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|first1=A.|last1=Averianov|first2=H.|last2=Sues|date=2012|title=Correlation of Late Cretaceous continental vertebrate assemblages in Middle and Central Asia|journal=Journal of Stratigraphy|volume=36|issue=2|pages=462–485|url=https://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/df17/104349a1f7fd4dfd76252f91817fe5f58fb6.pdf?_ga=2.179684836.1368930193.1572314200-1555398245.1565561157|access-date=2020-12-30|archive-date=2019-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190307103653/http://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/df17/104349a1f7fd4dfd76252f91817fe5f58fb6.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、與海洋接壤<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Funston|first1=G. F.|last2=Currie|first2=P. J.|last3=Ryan|first3=M. J.|last4=Dong|first4=Z.-M.|title=Birdlike growth and mixed-age flocks in avimimids (Theropoda, Oviraptorosauria)|date=2019|journal=Scientific Reports|volume=9|issue=18816|page=18816|doi=10.1038/s41598-019-55038-5|pmc=6906459|pmid=31827127}}</ref>的[[氾濫平原|氾濫平原]]，並如{{link-en|古土壤|Paleosol}}發展所示支持著廣泛的植被以及大量的[[植食性|植食性]]恐龍（如[[鴨嘴龍科|鴨嘴龍科]]）。<ref name=Itterbeeck2005/>

如同其他似鳥龍類，古似鳥龍可能是雜食性動物，具有角質[[鳥喙|嘴喙]]，從小哺乳類、植物、水果、蛋、到甚至是其他恐龍幼體都吃。<ref name=Norell2001>{{cite journal|last1=Norell|first1=M. A.|last2=Makovicky|first2=P. J.|last3=Currie|first3=P. J.|title=The beak of ostrich dinosaurs|journal=Nature|date=2001|volume=412|issue=6850|pages=873–874|doi=10.1038/35091139|pmid=11528466}}</ref><ref name=Barrett2005>{{cite journal|last1=Barrett|first1=P. M.|title=The diet of ostrich dinosaurs (Theropoda: Ornithomimosauria)|journal=Palaeontology|date=2005|volume=48|issue=2|pages=347–358|doi=10.1111/j.1475-4983.2005.00448.x}}</ref>

與古似鳥龍共棲的恐龍包括：其他獸腳類如[[暴龍超科|暴龍超科]]的[[獨龍|獨龍]]、[[鐮刀龍科|鐮刀龍科]]的[[二連龍|二連龍]]和[[內蒙古龍|內蒙古龍]]、[[偷蛋龍科|偷蛋龍科]]的[[巨盜龍|巨盜龍]]；植食性恐龍以[[鴨嘴龍類|鴨嘴龍類]]的[[巴克龍|巴克龍]]和[[計氏龍|計氏龍]]、[[蜥腳類|蜥腳類]]的[[蘇尼特龍|蘇尼特龍]]為代表。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Xing|first1=H.|last2=He|first2=Y.|last3=Li|first3=L.|last4=Xi|first4=D.|chapter=A review on the study of the stratigraphy, sedimentology, and paleontology of the Iren Dabasu Formation, Inner Mongolia|title=Proceedings of the Thirteenth Annual Meeting of the Chinese Society of Vertebrate Paleontology|publisher=China Ocean Press|year=2012|editor-last1=Wei|editor-first1=D.|location=Beijing|pages=1–44|url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/280545869|language=zh}}</ref>

